#: 
msgid "Allow visitors to self-register as new families."
msgstr "Luba külastajatel registreeruda uute peredena."

#. plugin:external-backup:section:5:content
#: 
msgid "Any WebDAV-compatible service works with this plugin:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (recommended)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (with WebDAV)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx with WebDAV module\n"
"\n"
"Note: Some services require app-specific passwords for WebDAV access."
msgstr "Kõik WebDAV-ühilduvad teenused töötavad selle pistikprogrammiga:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (soovitatav)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (WebDAV-iga)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx koos WebDAV-mooduliga\n"
"\n"
"Märkus: Mõned teenused nõuavad WebDAV-juurdepääsuks rakendusepõhiseid paroole."

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:title
#: 
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Autentimine"

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Authentication is required for API v2 if you've enabled it in OpenLP's Remote plugin settings. The plugin uses HTTP Basic Authentication. Most local network setups don't require authentication, but it's recommended for security."
msgstr "Autentimine on API v2 jaoks nõutav, kui olete selle OpenLP Remote-pistikprogrammi seadetes lubanud. Pistikprogramm kasutab HTTP-põhiautentimist. Enamik kohalike võrgu seadistusi ei nõua autentimist, kuid see on soovitatav turvalisuse tagamiseks."

#: 
msgid "Auto TLS"
msgstr "Automaatne TLS"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:2:title
#: 
msgid "Auto-Backup"
msgstr "Automaatne varukoopia"

#: 
msgid "BCC All Mail To"
msgstr "BCC kõik kirjad aadressile"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Before relying on external backups, test your connection:\n"
"1. Go to Plugins > External Backup\n"
"2. Click 'Test WebDAV Connection'\n"
"3. Verify you see a success message\n"
"\n"
"Common issues:\n"
"- 401/403 errors: Check username and password\n"
"- Connection timeout: Verify the endpoint URL is correct\n"
"- Certificate errors: Ensure the WebDAV server has a valid SSL certificate"
msgstr "Enne väliste varukoopiate kasutamist testige ühendust:\n"
"1. Minge Pistikprogrammid > Väline varukoopia\n"
"2. Klõpsake 'Testi WebDAV-ühendust'\n"
"3. Veenduge, et näete eduteadet\n"
"\n"
"Levinud probleemid:\n"
"- 401/403 vead: Kontrollige kasutajanime ja parooli\n"
"- Ühenduse ajalõpp: Veenduge, et lõpp-punkti URL on õige\n"
"- Sertifikaadi vead: Veenduge, et WebDAV-serveril on kehtiv SSL-sertifikaat"

